number.name: amount
number.label: Amount
number.description: The total amount of the deal

number.name: amount_in_home_currency
number.label: Amount in company currency
number.description: The amount of the deal, using the exchange rate, in your company's currency

number.name: days_to_close
number.label: Days to close
number.description: The number of days the deal took to close

number.name: hs_acv
number.label: Annual contract value
number.description: The annual contract value (ACV) of this deal.

number.name: hs_arr
number.label: Annual recurring revenue
number.description: The annual recurring revenue (ARR) of this deal.

number.name: hs_average_call_duration
number.label: Average call duration
number.description: The average call duration of calls associated to the deal

number.name: hs_closed_amount
number.label: Closed Deal Amount
number.description: Returns the amount if the deal is closed. Else, returns 0.

number.name: hs_closed_amount_in_home_currency
number.label: Closed deal amount in home currency
number.description: The amount in home currency that was closed for deals that were won.

number.name: hs_closed_deal_close_date
number.label: Closed Deal Close Date
number.description: Close date populated only if this deal is closed and valid

number.name: hs_closed_deal_create_date
number.label: Closed Deal Create Date
number.description: Create date populated only if this deal is closed

number.name: hs_closed_won_count
number.label: Closed won count
number.description: This property is 1 if the deal is closed won, otherwise 0.

number.name: hs_created_by_user_id
number.label: Created by user ID
number.description: The user who created this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

number.name: hs_days_to_close_raw
number.label: Days to close (without rounding)
number.description: The number of days the deal took to close, without rounding

number.name: hs_deal_registration_mrr
number.label: HubSpot Shared Deal MRR
number.description: MRR of the quote purchased for this Shared Deal.

number.name: hs_deal_score
number.label: Deal Score
number.description: The predictive deal score calculated by Hubspot AI to score the deal health

number.name: hs_deal_stage_probability
number.label: Deal probability
number.description: The probability a deal will close. This defaults to the deal stage probability setting.

number.name: hs_deal_stage_probability_shadow
number.label: Deal stage probability shadow
number.description: Fall back property for calculating the deal stage when no customer override exist.  Probability between 0 and 1 of deal stage. Defaults to 0 for unknown deal stages.

number.name: hs_duration
number.label: Duration
number.description: The duration between the create date and close date

number.name: hs_exchange_rate
number.label: Exchange rate
number.description: This is the exchange rate used to convert the deal amount into your company currency.

number.name: hs_forecast_amount
number.label: Forecast amount
number.description: The custom forecasted deal value calculated by multiplying the forecast probability and deal amount in your company’s currency.

number.name: hs_forecast_probability
number.label: Forecast probability
number.description: The custom percent probability a deal will close.

number.name: hs_is_closed_count
number.label: Is Closed (numeric)
number.description: This property is 1 if the deal is closed ("Closed Won" or "Closed Lost"), otherwise 0

number.name: hs_is_open_count
number.label: Is Open (numeric)
number.description: This property is 1 if the deal is not closed won or closed lost, otherwise 0

number.name: hs_latest_approval_status_approval_id
number.label: Latest Approval Status Approval ID
number.description: The ID of the approval object containing the latest approval status.

number.name: hs_likelihood_to_close
number.label: Likelihood to close by the close date
number.description: Hubspot predicted likelihood between 0 and 1 of the deal to close by the close date.

number.name: hs_manual_campaign_ids
number.label: Manual campaign ids
number.description: The campaign object ids of deals manually associated to campaigns

number.name: hs_mrr
number.label: Monthly recurring revenue
number.description: The monthly recurring revenue (MRR) of this deal.

number.name: hs_net_pipeline_impact
number.label: Net Pipeline Impact
number.description: This property is intended for measuring pipeline impact in the Deal Pipeline Waterfall report in Sales Analytics. It is dynamically calculated and utilized as a metric by the HistoricalReportingService.

number.name: hs_num_associated_active_deal_registrations
number.label: Number of Active Deal Registrations
number.description: The number of active deal registrations associated with this deal. This property is set automatically by HubSpot.

number.name: hs_num_associated_deal_registrations
number.label: Number of Deal Registrations
number.description: The number of deal registrations associated with this deal. This property is set automatically by HubSpot.

number.name: hs_num_associated_deal_splits

number.name: hs_number_of_call_engagements
number.label: Number of call engagements

number.name: hs_number_of_inbound_calls
number.label: Number of inbound calls
number.description: The number of inbound calls associated to the deal

number.name: hs_number_of_outbound_calls

number.name: hs_number_of_overdue_tasks

number.name: hs_number_of_scheduled_meetings

number.name: hs_object_id

number.name: hs_object_source_user_id

number.name: hs_open_amount_in_home_currency
number.label: Open amount in home currency
number.description: The amount of the open deal, using the exchange rate, in your home currency

number.name: hs_open_deal_create_date
number.label: Open deal create date
number.description: Create date populated only if this deal is open

number.name: hs_pinned_engagement_id
number.label: Pinned Engagement ID
number.description: The object ID of the current pinned engagement. This will only be shown if there is already an association to the engagement.

number.name: hs_predicted_amount
number.label: The predicted deal amount
number.description: Returns the multiplication of the deal amount times the predicted likelihood of the deal to close by the close date.

number.name: hs_predicted_amount_in_home_currency
number.label: The predicted deal amount in your company's currency
number.description: Returns the multiplication of the deal amount in your company's currency times the predicted likelihood of the deal to close by the close date.

number.name: hs_primary_associated_company
number.label: Primary Associated Company
number.description: Object Id of the Primary Associated Company.

number.name: hs_projected_amount
number.label: Weighted amount
number.description: Returns the multiplication of the amount times the probability of the deal closing.

number.name: hs_projected_amount_in_home_currency
number.label: Weighted amount in company currency
number.description: The deal’s amount in home currency multiplied by its probability of closing, which is determined based on the deal’s stage and the probability that was assigned to it in deal pipeline settings.

number.name: hs_source_object_id
number.label: Source Object ID
number.description: The ID of the object from which the data was migrated. This is set automatically during portal data migration.

number.name: hs_tcv

number.description: The total contract value (TCV) of this deal.

datetime.name: hubspot_owner_assigneddate
datetime.label: Owner assigned date
datetime.description: The most recent timestamp of when an owner was assigned to this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

datetime.name: notes_last_contacted
datetime.label: Last Contacted
datetime.description: The last time a call, sales email, or meeting was logged for this deal. This is set automatically by HubSpot based on user actions.

datetime.name: notes_last_updated
datetime.label: Last Activity Date
datetime.description: The last time a note, call, email, meeting, or task was logged for a deal. This is set automatically by HubSpot based on user actions in the deal record.

datetime.name: notes_next_activity_date
datetime.label: Next Activity Date
datetime.description: The date of the next upcoming activity for a deal. This property is set automatically by HubSpot based on user action. This includes logging a future call, sales email, or meeting using the Log feature, as well as creating a future task or scheduling a future meeting. This is updated automatically by HubSpot.

datetime.name: recurring_revenue_inactive_date
datetime.label: Recurring revenue inactive date
datetime.description: Date at which recurring revenue for this deal is no longer collected

bool.name: hs_has_empty_conditional_stage_properties
bool.label: Has Empty Conditional Stage Properties
bool.description: True if the deal is missing conditional stage property values required to progress to the next deal stage.  This is set automatically by HubSpot based on user actions in the deal record.

bool.name: hs_is_active_shared_deal
bool.label: Is Active Shared Deal
bool.description: Indicates if the current deal is an active shared deal. It is set automatically based on the value of hs_num_associated_active_deal_registrations.

bool.name: hs_is_closed
bool.label: Is Deal Closed?
bool.description: True if the deal was won or lost.

bool.name: hs_is_closed_lost
bool.label: Is closed lost
bool.description: True if the deal is in the closed lost state, false otherwise

bool.name: hs_is_closed_won
bool.label: Is Closed Won
bool.description: True if the deal is in the closed won state, false otherwise

bool.name: hs_is_deal_split
bool.label: Deal Split Added
bool.description: Indicates if the deal is split between multiple users.

bool.name: hs_is_in_first_deal_stage
bool.label: Is In First Deal Stage
bool.description: True if the deal is in the first stage of its pipeline. This is set automatically by HubSpot based on user actions in the deal record.

bool.name: hs_line_item_global_term_hs_discount_percentage_enabled
bool.label: Global Term Line Item Discount Percentage Enabled
bool.description: For internal HubSpot Application use only. Indicates if the Global term for the discount percentage is enabled.

bool.name: hs_line_item_global_term_hs_recurring_billing_period_enabled
bool.label: Global Term Line Item Recurring Billing Period Enabled
bool.description: For internal HubSpot Application use only. Indicates if the Global term for product recurring billing duration is enabled.

bool.name: hs_line_item_global_term_hs_recurring_billing_start_date_enabled
bool.label: Global Term Line Item Recurring Billing Start Date Enabled
bool.description: For internal HubSpot Application use only. Indicates if the Global term for recurring billing start date for a line item is enabled.

bool.name: hs_line_item_global_term_recurringbillingfrequency_enabled
bool.label: Global Term Line Item Recurring Billing Frequency Enabled
bool.description: For internal HubSpot Application use only. Indicates if the Global term for how frequently the product is billed is enabled

bool.name: hs_read_only
bool.label: Read only object
bool.description: Determines whether a record can be edited by a user.
